@end deffn

@geindex ghdl command line option; --wave<=FILENAME>
@anchor{using/Simulation cmdoption-ghdl-wave}@anchor{a0}
@deffn {Option} @w{-}@w{-}wave<=FILENAME>

Write the waveforms into a @cite{ghw} (GHdl Waveform) file.  Currently, all
