************ (sometimes skipped in small documents)
============
-------------------
‘’’’’’’’’’’’’’’’’’’’’’’’
@end example

@item 
It’s not required to write

@example
:samp:`code`
@end example

The default role for

@quotation

@example
`@w{`}…`@w{`}
@end example
@end quotation

is samp. @code{:samp:} is only required when you want to write italic text in code text.

@quotation

