@end quotation

@code{print 1+@emph{variable}}
@end quotation

Now, variable becomes italic.

Please simplify all usages of @code{…`to `}…`@w{`} for readability. Here are the regular expressions for an editor like Notepad++:


@itemize -

@item 
Search pattern:: @code{(.+?)}

@item 
